  ## Installation
  ```shell
    npm install
  ```
  
  
  ## Installation And Setup
  1. Clone the repo

  ```shell
  git@github.com:fondofhats/professional-readme-generator.git
  ```

  2. Move to the project root directory

```shell
  cd professional-readme-generator
```

3. Run npm install

```shell
npm install
```

4. Run Readme Generator

```shell
node index.js
```
